This is destroying @DeptofDefense’s buying power, affecting everything from servicemember benefits to maintenance, and more.

@POTUS’s FY23 budget must address this problem &amp; provide real growth for defense.

.@POTUS and his Administration continue to be surprised when the Taliban acts like the Taliban.

